prompt_text:
Analyze the following lead information and provide a scoring from 0-100 based on fit, engagement, company size, budget indicators, and timeline:

Company: {{company_name}}
Industry: {{industry}}
Contact: {{contact_name}}
Recent Activity: {{activity_summary}}

Provide: 1) Overall score 2) Score breakdown by category 3) Key strengths 4) Areas of concern 5) Recommended next action

Analyze the following commercial bid opportunity and recommend a go/no-go decision:

Project: {{project_name}}
Scope: {{scope_description}}
Budget: {{budget_range}}
Timeline: {{timeline}}
Competitors: {{estimated_competitors}}
Our Capacity: {{capacity_status}}

Provide: 1) Win probability estimate 2) Recommended bid price 3) Risk factors 4) Resource requirements 5) Final recommendation with reasoning

Evaluate if this lead qualifies for our {{product_type}} offering using the BANT framework:

Budget: {{budget_info}}
Authority: {{decision_maker_info}}
Need: {{stated_need}}
Timeline: {{implementation_timeline}}

Additional Context:
- Company Size: {{company_size}}
- Industry Fit: {{industry}}
- Current Solution: {{current_solution}}

Provide: 1) BANT score for each dimension 2) Overall qualification level (Hot/Warm/Cold) 3) Gap analysis 4) Nurture strategy if not ready 5) Next conversation topics

Design an automated workflow for {{process_name}} that reduces manual work by {{efficiency_target}}%.

Current Process: {{current_steps}}
Pain Points: {{pain_points}}
Available Tools: {{tool_stack}}
Team Skill Level: {{skill_level}}

Provide: 1) Automation architecture diagram 2) Step-by-step workflow 3) Decision trees/conditions 4) Error handling 5) Monitoring/alerts 6) Expected time savings 7) Implementation roadmap

Map the complete customer journey for {{customer_persona}} purchasing {{product_category}}:

Target Persona: {{persona_details}}
Price Range: {{price_sensitivity}}
Decision Timeline: {{timeline}}
Key Influencers: {{influencer_roles}}

Identify: 1) Awareness stage triggers 2) Consideration challenges 3) Decision factors 4) Post-purchase needs 5) Upsell opportunities 6) Touchpoints for each stage 7) Messaging for each stage

Develop a winning proposal strategy for {{prospect_name}} requesting {{deliverable}}:

Competing Against: {{competitors}}
Decision Criteria: {{stated_criteria}}
Budget: {{budget}}
Unique Advantage: {{our_advantage}}

Create: 1) Executive summary positioning 2) Proof of capability framework 3) Differentiation narrative 4) Risk mitigation strategy 5) Pricing justification 6) Timeline realism 7) Client success story alignment

Define capabilities and boundaries for a {{agent_type}} agent focused on {{primary_function}}:

Desired Outcomes: {{desired_outcomes}}
Data Sources: {{available_data}}
Domain Expertise: {{expertise_domain}}
Constraints: {{business_constraints}}

Specify: 1) Core responsibilities 2) Authority/decision-making limits 3) Required knowledge/tools 4) Success metrics 5) Escalation triggers 6) Error handling approach 7) Learning/improvement mechanisms
